  "title": "Senior QAQC Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:-</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct QAQC daily checks</li>\n  <li>Prepare monthly QAQC report for submission to Corporate QAQC Department</li>\n  <li>Conducting monthly QAQC Training to Sub-contractors</li>\n  <li>Issuance of QAQC Non-compliance to Sub-contractors</li>\n  <li>Provide QAQC observations on the defective work of the Sub-contractors to the site team and follow up</li>\n  <li>Attend monthly QAQC presentation and meeting at Corporate QAQC Department</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/ Diploma in Civil engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Min 5 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Good understanding of Quality practices</li>\n  <li>Architectural-trained or Structural-trained work experience will be preferred</li>\n</ul>",
